{"tid":1858914,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"淋病應對醫護罷工對策 = 拖","createTime":"2020-02-03T03:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T07:21:56.000Z","uid":194298,"like":58,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"9662eb8d6da181044723d4b4da906f9152c8bbc0","tid":1858914,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:38:11.000Z","msg":"港共指示食衛局配合醫管局調配人手，裝作服務仍然維持正常<br />\n頭幾日甚至一星期可能真係無問題，見唔到大影響<br />\n一直向外宣稱罷工無成效 + 帶風向譴責醫護<br />\n同應對示威用同一手法，不斷放廣告想分化和勇，扮承受得到衝擊<br />\n此時如果醫護個心一動搖，開始諗自己既行動係咪真係無效，心軟，復工，就會兵敗如山倒<br />\n所以罷工一旦開始，就要堅持，直至<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">最終目標 - 全面封關</span></span> 達成，否則絕不退讓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">感激醫護，全香港市民企係你地果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1fdb5d70c83a63f69bbf25841a196f990165add0","tid":1858914,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:38:49.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"14aa3547d7792469c5e9b5af6ef2738e3ca9471a","tid":1858914,"uid":72457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vmJsuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vmJsuk.jpg&h=30c95e8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mRDS5f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmRDS5f2.jpg&h=b33d1b68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdc2a9a3880234db8b954c26d097a0588d6a3d8a","tid":1858914,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:40:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最終目標唔止係全面封關啊</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156d21b4b9c27e35960899d323fc71a8c1cf5829","tid":1858914,"uid":129169,"like":3,"dislike":0,